uardo Romero]]\n|-\n|align=center|6\n|align=right|24 Nov 2002<br>([[2003 European Tour|2003]] season)\n|[[BMW Asian Open]]<sup>1</sup>\n|\u221215 (66-70-68-69=273)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|IND}} [[Jyoti Randhawa]]\n|-\n|align=center|7\n|align=right|18 May 2003\n|[[Deutsche Bank - SAP Open TPC of Europe]]\n|\u221219 (65-66-70-68=269)\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|DNK}} [[Thomas Bj\u00f8rn]]\n|-\n|align=center|8\n|align=right|7 Dec 2003<br>([[2004 European Tour|2004]] season)\n|[[Omega Hong Kong Open]]<sup>1</sup>\n|\u221213 (66-75-64-70=275)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|RSA}} [[Hennie Otto]]\n|-\n|align=center|9\n|align=right|12 Sep 2004\n|[[Linde German Masters]]\n|\u221211 (67-69-67-66=269)\n|3 strokes\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Nick O'Hern]]\n|-\n|align=center|10\n|align=right|8 Oct [[2006 European Tour|2006]]\n|[[Alfred Dunhill Links Championship]] <small>(2)</small>\n|\u221217 (66-69-68-68=271)\n|5 strokes\n|{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Bradley Dredge]], {{flagicon|USA}} [[Edward Loar]],<br>{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Anthony Wall]]\n|-\n|align=center|11\n|align=right|20 May [[2007 European Tour|2007]]\n|[[Irish Open (golf)|Irish Open]]\n|\u22125 (73-68-71-71=283)\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Bradley Dredge]]\n|-style=\"background:#e5d1cb;\"\n|align=center|12\n|align=right|22 Jul 2007\n|'''[[2007 Open Championship|The Open Championship]]'''\n|\u22127 (69-73-68-67=277)\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sergio Garc\u00eda]]\n|-style=\"background:#e5d1cb;\"\n|align=center|13\n|align=right|20 Jul [[2008 European Tour|2008]]\n|'''[[2008 Open Championship|The Open Championship]]''' <small>(2)</small>\n| +3 (74-68-72-69=283)\n|4 strokes\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ian Poulter]]\n|-style=\"background:#e5d1cb;\"\n|align=center|14\n|align=right|10 Aug 2008\n|'''[[2008 PGA Championship|PGA Championship]]'''\n|\u22123 (71-74-66-66=277)\n|2 strokes\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sergio Garc\u00eda]], {{flagicon|USA}} [[Ben Curtis (golfer)|Ben Curtis]]\n|-\n|align=center|15\n|align=right|23 Oct [[2016 European Tour|2016]]\n|[[Portugal Masters]]\n|\u221223 (66-63-67-65=261)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Andy Sullivan (golfer)|Andy Sullivan]]\n|}\n\n<sup>1</sup>Co-sanctioned by the  [[Asian Tour]]\n\n'''European Tour playoff record (4\u20134)'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n!No.!!Year!!Tournament!!Opponent(s)!!Result\n|-style=\"background:#F2C1D1;\"\n|align=center|1\n|[[1999 European Tour|1999]]\n|[[Linde German Masters]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sergio Garc\u00eda]], {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Ian Woosnam]]\n|Garc\u00eda won with birdie on second extra hole<br>Woosnam eliminated by par on first hole\n|-style=\"background:#F2C1D1;\"\n|align=center|2\n|[[2000 European Tour|2000]]\n|[[Brazil Rio de Janeiro 500 Years Open]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Roger Chapman (golfer)|Roger Chapman]]\n|Lost to par on second extra hole\n|-style=\"background:#F2C1D1;\"\n|align=center|3\n|[[2001 European Tour|2001]]\n|[[Carlsberg Malaysian Open]]\n|{{flagicon|FJI}} [[Vijay Singh]]\n|Lost to birdie on third extra hole\n|-style=\"background:#D0F0C0;\"\n|align=center|4\n|[[2002 European Tour|2002]]\n|[[Dunhill Links Championship]]\n|{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Eduardo Romero]]\n|Won with birdie on second extra hole\n|-style=\"background:#D0F0C0;\"\n|align=center|5\n|[[2003 European Tour|2003]]\n|[[Deutsche Bank - SAP Open TPC of Europe]]\n|{{flagicon|DNK}} [[Thomas Bj\u00f8rn]]\n|Won with par on first extra hole\n|-style=\"background:#F2C1D1;\"\n|align=center|6\n|[[2006 European Tour|2006]]\n|[[BMW International Open]]\n|{{flagicon|ZAF}} [[Retief Goosen]], {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Henrik Stenson]]\n|Stenson won with eagle on first extra hole\n|-style=\"background:#D0F0C0;\"\n|align=center|7\n|[[2007 European Tour|2007]]\n|[[Irish Open (golf)|Irish Open]]\n|{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Bradley Dredge]]\n|Won with par on first extra hole\n|-style=\"background:#D0F0C0;\"\n|align=center|8\n|2007\n|'''[[2007 Open Championship|The Open Championship]]'''\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sergio Garc\u00eda]]\n|Won four-hole aggregate playoff;<br>Harring